title: Gay Puree
description:
This classic animated movie is about a feline named Mewsette, who sets out to Paris to find the high life, to find herself, and to basically get out of the country. Her long time love, Jaun Tom, and his companion, Robspierre, give chase. Mewsette runs into Meowrice, who has all kinds of devious plans for this unsuspecting country feline.
Will Jaun Tom and Robspierre manage to find Mewsette in the vast expanse that is Paris? And will they manage to save her from the plans laid by Meowrice?

This movie was made in 1962, and is a high quality MP4 file
